dct_title_s: St. Augustine Bay and Tullear harbour, on the west coast of Madagascar
dct_description_sm: Hydrographic chart of west coast of Madagascar, showing Tullear and St. Augustine Bay; relief shown by hachures and bathymetric soundings. "692."
